install using simplecv repository
--
sudo apt-get install ipython python-opencv python-scipy python-numpy python-pygame python-setuptools git
git clone https://github.com/sightmachine/SimpleCV.git
cd Downloads
sudo dpkg -i ./SimpleCV-1.3.deb // <<put location of the downloaded file from the location >>

cd SimpleCV
sudo pip install -r requirements.txt // this line may not work
sudo python setup.py install



+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
install using pip
--
sudo apt-get install ipython python-opencv python-scipy python-numpy python-pygame python-setuptools python-pip
sudo pip install https://github.com/sightmachine/SimpleCV/zipball/develop
